latestIgtvVideos.title: The Residence with Etihad Airways
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Here’s a little sneak peek into our flight with @etihadairways inside ‘The Residence’. This was our last flight of the year and was such an amazing way to close out the decade, after such incredible adventures! Truly a once in a lifetime experience that we’ll never forget. #Etihad #A380 #sponsored

latestIgtvVideos.title: Wanderlust in The Maldives.
latestIgtvVideos.caption: #WCOxTaraMilkTea ✨ Created for the wanderlust dreamers, it felt so special to be wearing my collection pieces for our final trip of the year (and the decade) in one of the most beautiful places on earth. These pieces mean so much to me and have been all around the world for the last half year, and I’m excited to wear them well into the new decade. @wanderlustandco ✨

latestPosts.caption:
Everyone—please give a warm welcome to @taramilktea 😍❤️🩷Can you believe we’ve been internet friends for years and finally met on this Revolve trip? As soon as we knew we were both coming, we had to plan a little video moment together. If you follow her (which I’m sure you do), you already know how amazing her content is.
She told me she’s dying to visit Taiwan—I said, you have to! Can you imagine how beautiful she’d make it look? 😍❤️🩷 @revolve #revolvefestival 
-
影片一定要看到最後🩷
各位觀眾～隆重歡迎 @taramilktea 😍
天啊我們當了網友超級多年
終於在這次 @Revolve 出差活動見面了
當我們知道彼此今年都有參加的時候就立刻訊息
然後相約一起拍這部可愛的影片🥰

誰也有Follow她？
應該都對她的社群內容作品不陌生吧！？
她說她真的超想來台灣
我說你一定要來
她一定也可以把台灣拍得超美😍
你們說是吧～

歡迎可以留言英文讓她知道你們也很喜歡她😙

P.S. 她說台語真的也是超可愛😂
